        <td width="262" style="padding:5px"><p align="center"><font color="#006600"><strong><font size="5">MGOA Announces over a 500% Increase in Quarterly Revenue and GROWING!!! </font></strong></font></p>
          <p>As Megola moves forward in structuring their distribution system, manufacturing and alliances, it is having a direct affect on their revenue stream. Megola will continue to experience strong growth as its distribution network and product lines expand. With alliances with companies like BuyMax LLC and with new product trials currently under way, Megola continues to strive towards its objective of being recognized as a valuable asset in the environmental solution marketplace. </p>
          <table width="100%"  border="1" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#3964B3">
            <tr>
              <td><h4 align="center"><font color="#FFFFFF">*WHY CONSIDER MEGOLA*</font></h4>
                <ul>
                  <font color="#FFFFFF"><li><strong>Water Treatment Industry is Explodiong </strong></li></font>
